-- Apa Canal of Romania Awards Waterworks Contract to Vega’93
-- B y   I r i n a   S a v u
-- 2013-03-27T09:24:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-27/apa-canal-of-romania-awards-waterworks-contract-to-vega-93.html
Apa Canal SA, a Romanian water
utility, awarded an 83.4 million lei ($24 million) contract to
 Vega’93 SRL  to upgrade its network in the east of the country.  The work includes improving water and sewage pipelines,
pumping stations and water-treatment plants, as well as
engineering design services in five towns in Galati County, Apa
Canal said in a  notice  on the European Union’s tender website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Irina Savu in Bucharest at 
 isavu@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  